          <mainBody>
            <p eId="annex_1_p_8"><b>Annex A - Hansard References</b></p>
            <blockContainer>
              <num>39 </num>
              <p>The following table sets out the dates and Hansard references for each stage of the Act's passage through Parliament.</p>
            </blockContainer>
            <table uk:widths="1.72in 1.45in 3.13in">
              <tr>
                <th>
                  <p><b>Stage</b></p>
                </th>
                <th>
                  <p><b>Date</b></p>
                </th>
                <th>
                  <p><b>Hansard Reference</b></p>
                </th>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td colspan="3">
                  <p><i>House of Lords</i></p>
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>
                  <p>Introduction</p>
                </td>
                <td>
                  <p>13 May 2021</p>
                </td>
                <td>
                  <p><a href="https://hansard.parliament.uk/Lords/2021-05-13/debates/987038BA-23FA-4226-96FE-A6FA318FE1B7/AnimalWelfare(Sentience)Bill(HL)"><u>Vol. 812 Col. 166</u></a></p>
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>
                  <p>Second Reading</p>
